videos.headline: Chase burns safety for 34-yard TD
videos.description: Joe Burrow connects with Ja'Marr Chase down the sideline for a 34-yard LSU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Chase burns safety for 34-yard TD) 2019/11/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Burrow throws 3rd TD to Jefferson
